# Pyramid Intervals [Running] (2026-03-12)
@ focus: VO2max development

> Total work: 18min at Z4. Keep effort consistent across pyramids.

- Warmup 10min @Z1
- 3x:
  @ rest_between_rounds: 2min
  - 2x:
    - Run 30s @Z4
    - Recover 30s @Z1
  - Run 1min @Z4
  - Recover 1min @Z1
  - 2x:
    - Run 30s @Z4
    - Recover 30s @Z1
- Cooldown 10min @Z1
